                                text="&lt;p>The workflow extension enables the declaration of collaborative processes. The definition of a workflow is very flexible. Workflow steps are defined by simple tasks with decision options. These tasks can then be linked to become a workflow. Interactive steps of a workflow are shown in the inbox view of the assigned users or groups.&lt;/p>"
